Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:06.27,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,2500)}ReLIFE Experiment Contract
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:06.27,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,ReLIFE Laboratory is an organization\Nthat is developing a program
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:11.03,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,to rehabilitate people who have dropped out\Nof society: your so-called NEETs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:18.16,Flashback Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For a year starting this spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.87,Flashback Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we want you to be a student,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.70,Flashback Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and go back to high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.04,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I've come too far to turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.05,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you're on!\NI'll do this ReLIFE thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:06.02,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}Communication Skills: Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.52,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't handle waking up this early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.36,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Based on yesterday's tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.03,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,the 3-3 class reps for the first term are:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:20.74,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oga-kun for the boys, \Nand Hishiro-san for the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.28,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Great to be working with you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.99,Main Dialogue Top,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.21,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I failed all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.84,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe Oga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.80,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:39.05,Main Dialogue Top,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,With these two leading you,\NI hope you have a fun first term.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.80,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But he's so showy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.80,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:44.97,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with her? She looks furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:50.14,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,But this year, she's in the same class as\NHishiro-san, the top scorer in our grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:53.61,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,521)}So she's all fired up now\Nand couldn't call in sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:57.07,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she must be mad\Nshe didn't top the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.15,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure working with ya, Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:00.57,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:06.04,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.66,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Drop by the staff room later\Nto pick up your silver pins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.71,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:09.71,Flashback Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.71,Main Dialogue,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.25,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, huh, Kariu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:17.13,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you rubbing salt into her wound?\NGet a clue, Oga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.63,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, you did have a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.01,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Hope you can take her on\N at full strength next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:27.01,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. It was all my fault,\Nincluding my failure to take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.22,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna use the cold as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:31.06,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I just wasn't as good as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.02,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.86,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You're so indifferent. Not cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.77,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off already, Oga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.11,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, I'm not cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:42.15,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're glad you don't\Nhave to work with me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.53,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:46.03,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.08,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the persecution complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.12,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Just drop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.33,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?\NI was trying to cheer you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.67,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,By talking down to me? Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.59,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.59,Main Dialogue Top,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so pissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.09,Main Dialogue Top,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.34,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I almost forgot. About the tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:04.68,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,As always, if you failed even one,\N you're going to take make-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:07.68,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll keep taking them\Nuntil you score higher than 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.44,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Study hard so you pass the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:16.69,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fifty or more on all of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.44,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Endless make-ups!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.40,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,What? You failed one, Kaizaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:24.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Not "one." All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.07,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, people like that actually exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:29.70,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, which was the worst?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:32.37,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Math. I got a four.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\i1}excuse{\i0} me for getting a four!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.75,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Not everyone's as smart as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.01,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.55,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's the effort that counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.05,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Work hard, Kaizaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.55,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.01,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Same to the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.43,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.06,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I could tutor you, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.56,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry if I'm being too nosy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.86,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,but with those scores, who knows\Nwhen you'll escape the make-up loop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:06.20,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not sure if I should\Nfeel insulted or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.07,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.33,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get in on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:15.21,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Onoya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.67,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.67,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.67,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.50,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Another complete failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.88,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.02,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.06,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Headed for the cafeteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.73,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna eat lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.98,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.48,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do at times like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:46.11,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be glad not to eat alone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.16,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,At this age, a boy and \Na girl eating together...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.58,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Won't people make fun of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.83,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Can I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.46,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,We can get started on\N our test prep planning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.04,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good idea! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.54,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Showga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.34,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You coming, Kariu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:06.88,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eating with Honoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.14,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,With Tamarai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.64,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, from the volleyball team?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.35,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.48,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna swing by the \Nstaff room for the silver pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.60,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You know where the cafeteria is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.65,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. We'll grab seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.69,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is a silver pin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.15,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I think it's...\N the symbol of the class rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.00,sign_9495_106_Bread,,0000,0000,0000,,Bread
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.00,sign_9495_107_Noodles,,0000,0000,0000,,Noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.00,sign_9495_108_Rice_Bowls,,0000,0000,0000,,Sets/Bowls
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.00,sign_9495_109_Register,,0000,0000,0000,,Register
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.50,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:43.50,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Say, you and Kariu-san\Nseem awfully close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:47.63,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Is she, like, your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.34,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She came right out and asked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.39,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:56.39,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually wondering the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.23,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Fess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.15,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.56,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What gave you that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're not dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.53,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought I read people better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.95,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,One other question, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:16.70,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,If she's not your girlfriend,\N what's with the matching earrings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.20,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Earrings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.54,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you actually noticed that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.79,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in first year...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.88,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,My brother insisted on piercing my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.88,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,It hurt so much,\N I didn't let him do the other ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:34.05,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,So the other half of this pair\Nis gonna go unused. Want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.93,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously trying to fob it off on me\Nbecause you don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.60,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:46.98,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.36,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,It's free, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.20,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,But you play volleyball...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.16,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.74,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Are you giving it to me or not?\NMake up your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.33,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I am! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.41,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.46,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Since you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.83,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gratefully accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:10.55,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,And she came in the very next day \Nwith her ear pierced! Hilarious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.09,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:16.22,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,If you asked her if we were dating, \NKariu would go berserk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.01,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.89,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,He might be book smart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:24.06,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,but he's the furthest thing from\Nan exemplary high school boy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. Total waste of a handsome face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.44,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.53,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.48,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:33.03,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You should read more modern lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:38.62,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Focus your studies on comprehending \Nthe emotions of the characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:42.00,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what? Why am I\N being assigned homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.45,Main Dialogue Top,Lunchlady,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.79,Main Dialogue Top,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we please work it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.12,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to prepping\N for the make-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:43.91,Main Dialogue Top,Lunchlady,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.29,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.50,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's the other class rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.09,Main Dialogue Top,Lunchlady,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.55,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.76,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.01,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go see why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.05,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:58.26,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the staff room\N and be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.10,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Hishiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.39,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's the guy who got a four.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.19,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.73,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,The cigarettes guy, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.98,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.65,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It left quite the impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.36,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, are you in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:20.24,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring any money out of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:26.83,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I said to wait while I got the silver pin,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:29.50,Cafetaria Head,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1777,1)}Students with silver pins are to state their name and class every time.\N{\fs14}And please wait in line like the others.\N - Cafeteria Head
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.50,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,but they'd already made the ramen, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.80,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Help, I need an interpreter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.76,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:40.05,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you forgot your money\N and can't buy lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.81,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.35,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't bring any.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.68,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.39,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:47.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.31,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Borrow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Pay me back whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.53,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:59.24,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Most things here don't cost\N more than 300 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:03.20,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,And I think 1,000 yen is a pretty\Nlarge sum for a high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.33,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,How can you lend me\N that much money so casually?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.71,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.71,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,...you're a grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.92,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I just happen \Nto have extra today! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:23.93,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It was an impulse, \Nbut I just took a high school girl's hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:28.69,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take you up on your kind offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.06,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.94,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:45.24,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What am I getting worked up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.71,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She's in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.17,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.42,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.46,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.55,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Very cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.38,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Though you're not at all book smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.76,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Knock that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.72,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She forgot her lunch money, \Nso I loaned her some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.26,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Last year's best student\Nis a bit of a ditz, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:09.18,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's probably just because\Nshe doesn't have her silver pin yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.77,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why her silver pin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:15.32,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,When you've got this,\Nyou can eat here for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.19,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:21.11,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,We also get commute allowance,\Ntuition exemption, and all sorts of perks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's pretty sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.91,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll never even\Nget a sniff of all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.54,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.92,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu was trying for the silver pin—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.04,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,No, she wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.17,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Onoya-san, you're harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.21,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Call me An.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.34,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.97,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Then, An-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.30,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to call me Kazu-kun—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.47,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stick with Oga-kun. It's easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.98,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,A cell phone at school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,They'll confiscate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.27,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,I read the school rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.27,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't banned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:59.99,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta keep 'em off or\Non vibrate in class, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.24,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.20,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get your number?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.16,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:11.83,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,In my day, if you brought one in, \Nthey'd take it for a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.17,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even yell at you now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.00,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Arata-kun, what's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.38,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,You should call me An, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.30,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. An, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.89,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You just dropped the \Nhonorific like it was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.85,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprisingly good with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:31.56,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.40,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,You're just weirdly naive, Oga-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.57,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Apology Letter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.24,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,An apology letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:50.58,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote something, but is it good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:53.50,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I have written plenty\Nof these for work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.21,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,The 1,000 yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.59,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,score of four,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.92,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,and cigarette guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:05.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, don't remember me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:08.47,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I couldn't recall your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.22,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But you're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.60,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's unrelated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.10,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kaizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.73,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.74,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've memorized it. I'm Hishiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:26.49,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:29.24,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think you used it at lunch, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.45,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,We did introductions yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.58,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,and you were introduced in \Nthis morning's homeroom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.37,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:36.92,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But you're dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.63,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.59,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say everything you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:43.84,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. I won't say it anymore,\Neven if that's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.09,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.43,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Staff Room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.80,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what were\Nyou doing in the staff room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.56,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you get in trouble, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.31,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you actually mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.06,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. That was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.73,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I came to pick up my silver pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.78,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Also, there was something \NI didn't understand on the tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.61,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,so I asked about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:07.07,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa. You sure are serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:13.16,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Am I a serious, boring girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.20,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:20.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you topped the grade last year, \Nso I just thought, "No wonder."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.71,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry if I offended you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.67,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should be the one apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:29.76,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,B-By the way, why do you \Nspeak so formally to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:34.14,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm a delinquent\N or scary or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.89,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:39.60,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,because it feels like she thinks I'm older,\Nand that's giving me heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.73,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She said as much at lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:42.73,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.98,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I talk to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.53,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.03,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.28,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Does that make me unapproachable?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.08,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,People tell me that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:59.83,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even at this age,\NI don't have any close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.75,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that was a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.21,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently society does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.59,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I keep thinking I need to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.51,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,but I have no idea where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.60,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It would help if you could tell me honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.69,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really unapproachable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:23.86,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly speaking, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:29.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But I also feel like \Nyou'd be worth getting to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:34.12,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno, maybe try smiling a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.12,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.66,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.00,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.25,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,You just freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:47.63,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, it just wasn't \Nwhat I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.88,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Then... like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.72,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.93,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No more! Abandon the smile strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.76,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make enemies, not friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:59.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't even manage a polite smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.73,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in trouble in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.31,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't have to rush things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:06.69,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make friends in time, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:11.61,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:12.74,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Did I put my foot in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:16.91,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:21.37,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,The future I assumed I would have
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.29,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,never came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.01,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'd rush things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.01,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,This year is my last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.81,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,We're third years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:47.56,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kept you talking. \NWe'd better get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:51.40,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:55.20,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.24,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,...your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:01.29,Huh Sign,,0001,0494,0139,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:16:59.91,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.29,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Can you have... my phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:05.25,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not sure how to respond to\Nthis sudden attempt to mug me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.50,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.71,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Fill in the blanks, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:11.51,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.13,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.76,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:19.10,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know your phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.64,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I want to be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:29.90,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to take the first step \Ntoward not being a friendless loner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.48,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.15,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Figure that much out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:35.95,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,You really are dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.37,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for not guessing all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.41,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But when you put it that clearly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:47.62,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,it won't be misunderstood, and I doubt \Nanyone would turn you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.71,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:56.34,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like an idiot, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:59.39,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Would you drop the insults \Nabout my intelligence already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:06.10,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,You also seem like someone \Nworth getting to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:09.65,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Would you look at that?\N You can smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.90,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I see. For better or worse,\Nshe's an utterly straightforward girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You smiled when I loaned you \Nthat 1,000 yen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.49,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.91,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but don't try and force it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.63,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Math's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:44.93,Flashback Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(564,1)}It's especially easy to \Nget hooked at your age!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:46.56,Flashback Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,727(}You won't be able to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.94,sign_27116_370_Yoake,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoake
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.94,sign_27116_371_Call,,0000,0000,0000,,Call
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:55.48,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:56.69,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:01.20,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, only your exterior looks young,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.49,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,so that's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:08.25,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll probably find it hard to\Nbuy them with your appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.09,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,May be a good time to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:16.76,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to shake the smell, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.97,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You just got Hishiro-san to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.93,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Can't have her turning against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What? You were watch—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.77,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Is she your type?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:27.81,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.94,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Be nice to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.40,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the same class with her last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.69,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,and she was alone the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.90,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But, like I told you from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:44.28,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,after your one-year ReLIFE period is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:50.66,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,classmates, teachers, and anyone\Nyou dealt with will forget about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:56.88,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,This is because 17-year-old \NKaizaki does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:20:01.97,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But your own memories \Nwill remain, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:06.14,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,If we erased those, \Nthere'd be no point to the ReLIFE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.06,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:11.23,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell anyone else about ReLIFE,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.94,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,the experiment will end immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.69,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll wipe my memories and throw me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.40,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.69,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You can't talk about this. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:23.57,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, you'll find yourself wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:28.41,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,how you got to be twenty-eight\N without remembering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:30.66,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,So be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.59,sign_29833_403_Hishiro_Chizuru_,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}{\an2}Hishiro Chizuru\NNew message\NClose View
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:51.77,sign_29833_404_Hishiro_Chizuru,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Hishiro Chizuru
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.26,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. This is Hishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:51.77,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:55.69,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to return the 1,000 yen tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.77,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to knowing you further.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.32,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a business e-mail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.70,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, a sticker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.49,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.08,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:11.33,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for adding me on LIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.83,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, this sticker of the sorry cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.09,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It kinda looks like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:25.55,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh, she's gonna get mad at me \Nfor saying dumb crap again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:28.76,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean it in a bad way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.06,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno if she'll get that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.31,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.02,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I did not see that coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:40.69,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's pretty weird.\NAnd adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:40.01,Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.04,0:23:28.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Having ramen for lunch, Hishiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:30.43,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I only eat tonkotsu ramen\N at the cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:32.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What, every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:34.16,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. But the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:36.93,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into some trouble\Ndue to not having my silver pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:40.01,Next Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Old Now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:38.71,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be careful, Oga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:39.69,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
